T-Awards-Photo-by-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Will-Smith-at-the-2024-BET-Awards-Photo-by-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Will-Smith-at-the-2024-BET-Awards-Photo-by-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Will-Smith-at-the-2024-BET-Awards-Photo-by-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Will-Smith-at-the-2024-BET-Awards-Photo-by-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Will-Smith-at-the-2024-BET-Awards-Photo-by-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">威尔·史密斯 (Will Smith)</a>继在 2022 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼上与克里斯·洛克 (Chris Rock) 发生广为人知的掌掴事件后，于昨天（6 月 30 日）在洛杉矶举行的 BET 颁奖典礼上复出。</p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/bad-boys-ride-or-die-review-will-smith-3762339"><b>《坏男孩：骑行或死亡》评论：愚蠢的侦探在方向盘上睡着了</b></a></li></ul><p>史密斯在仪式上表演了他的新歌“You Can Make It”。在舞台上，史密斯站在火圈中，周围的环境就像世界末日的风景。在他身后，屏幕上升起了一轮巨大的太阳。</p><p>在周日的表演开始时，史密斯告诉观众：“我不知道现在谁需要听到这个，但无论你的生活中发生什么，我都会在这里告诉你，你可以做到。”</p><p>这首歌的歌词包括：“<i>你必须忍受的地狱越黑暗，你享受的天堂就越明亮</i>……<i>跌得越重，你飞得越高，当魔鬼关上门时，上帝会打开一扇窗。”</i></p><p> <i>“相信我，他们试图让威尔·史密斯流血，在事后看来，我看到逆境是一份礼物。”</i></p><p>您可以在这里观看表演： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C83LqEbp3qV/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; m